    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274916</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Klarth&gt;さん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mister &lt;Klarth&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274996</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>もういいっ！
おまえとなんて
やっていられるか！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's it! I've had ENOUGH of your crap!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275048</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>勝手にすれば！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're so selfish!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275104</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、勝手にするさ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, I'm sure I am the selfish one!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275164</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>君たちは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You guys...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275164</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……行くぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Let's just go.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275232</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>あっ……行くって……
どこへ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>G-go? Go where?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275284</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>行っちゃった……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And he's gone...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275328</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>クルー……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kuru...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275388</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……あら、あなたたち……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...If it isn't everyone...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275444</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……あの……その……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We...uh...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275532</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>……うふふ……
みっともないとこ、
見せちゃったかしら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Haha, you seen something unbecoming of an adult relationship...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275588</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ケンカ……したのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You were...fighting?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275756</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>まぁね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You could say that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275756</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>ダメね、何年たっても、
あの人とはケンカしてばっか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No matter how old he is, all he does is bicker.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275756</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>大体、あの人のこと、
理解してるけど、やっぱり
まだぶつかることもあるわね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In essence, I understand him. I really do. But I can't help but enter arguments.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275828</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>オレと&lt;Mel&gt;だって、
ケンカばっかだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Me and &lt;Mel&gt; always fight about stuff.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275940</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>だって、ひとこと、言わずには
いられないことばっかり
&lt;Dio&gt;がやるからでしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But after we have nothing else to say we don't argue anymore.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276128</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>そういうこと、かもね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I suppose that's how arguing work...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276128</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>人間同士、何も言わないで
互いの関係は築けない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's the essence of human relationships. We wouldn't be able to bond if we didn't talk...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276128</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>口を開けば、考えの違いで
ぶつかるのは、さけられない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When we talk and we share different feelings on the matter we can't help but argue...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276128</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>以心伝心って
難しいわよねぇ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It really is hard to reach a tacit understanding...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276232</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>あ……
へんな話しちゃったわね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh... Sorry for thinking out loud...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276232</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>とにかく……あの人の
ことよろしくね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Give my best regards to that man.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276284</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>よろしくって……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Give him...your regards?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276424</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>たぶん、あの人、少し、
頭を冷やしたいって
思ってるだろうから……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Perhaps that man needs some time to cool his head...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276424</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>私もたまには
ひとりになりたいしね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Once in a while I'd like to be on my own, too...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
